      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Breaking the Ice",
        "Client": "Master Utsushi",
        "Description": "There\u0027s a Lunagaron in the Shrine\r\nRuins that\u0027s just beggin\u0027 for a thrashin\u0027,\r\nand you can be sure as shurikens,\r\nI\u0027m ready to give it one! Wanna go\r\nget gnarly on that pup? Last time\r\nyou showed me up, but not today!\r\nTime for the master to prove his title!",
